title: Pluralsight - Introduction to Joomla
description: Content Management Systems (CMS) are great options for website development, and for simple or complex website solutions. If you are considering a CMS, Joomla! might well be the system you are looking for. With Joomla! you can build a simple website or blog, or build complex applications like a membership site, an e-commerce store, a movie or music database, and more.
